WEBVTT

00:03.807 --> 00:05.491
I love the snow,...

00:05.704 --> 00:08.688
...but I also really, really love it when it rains.

00:10.192 --> 00:12.414
It's raining, it's pouring.

00:12.539 --> 00:14.574
The old man is snoring.

00:14.739 --> 00:16.617
He went to bed and bumped his head...

00:16.713 --> 00:18.937
...and couldn't get up in the morning.

00:19.522 --> 00:21.059
Let's sing it one more time.

00:22.125 --> 00:24.306
It's raining, it's pouring.

00:24.436 --> 00:26.351
The old man is snoring.

00:26.465 --> 00:28.323
He went to bed and bumped his head...

00:28.457 --> 00:30.513
...and couldn't get up in the morning.

00:30.758 --> 00:33.618
Thank you for singing with us. Bye!

